) Caper (U.S.)', 'Meta Platforms is due Wednesday night and Apple (AAPL), Amazon.com (AMZN) and Google parent Alphabet (GOOGL) are on tap Thursday night, along with hundreds of others.

Those earnings reports could roil the major indexes as well as sectors and, of course, individual names.']
